it */\n\tflex-wrap: wrap;\n\tjustify-content: space-between;\n\talign-items: flex-start;\n}\n.card {\n\twidth: 45%;\n\tmin-width: 350px;\n\tpadding: 5px;\n\tdisplay: flex;\n\taling-items: flex-start;\n\tborder-radius: 5px;\n\tbox-shadow: 0 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n}\n\n.card__image {\n\twidth: 40%;\n}\n\n.card__content {\n\twidth: 60%;\n\tpadding-top: 20px;\n}\n.card__description {\n\tmargin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n.card__price {\n\tfont-size: 18px;\n\tcolor: teal;\n\tmargin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.btn {\n\tdisplay: inline-block;\n\tpadding: 8px 25px;\n\tfont-size: 1rem;\n\ttext-decoration: none;\n\tbackground-color: cadetblue;\n\tcolor: white;\n\tborder-radius: 5px;\n\ttransition: opacity 400ms linear;\n}\n\n.btn:hover {\n\topacity: 0.8;\n}\n\n```  \nNow the interesting part:  \nAdd truncate class to the second card__description\n```html\n<div class=\"card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"card__image\">\n\t\t\t<img src=\"https://lekorna.com/images/products/yummy-cup2.png\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"card__content\">\n\t\t\t<!-- Right here\t-->\n\t\t\t<p class=\"card__description truncate\">Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Voluptatum facilis voluptatem impedit nemo consequatur voluptates ipsum a voluptas quo deserunt?</p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"card__price\">35.99$</p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Buy</a>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n```\n\nand css\n```css\n.truncate {\n\t/* Avoids text being rendered outside the container */\n\twidth: 100%;\n\toverflow: hidden;\n\t/* Avoid text going to multiple lines */\n\twhite-space: nowrap;\n\t/* Sets the ... once the text overflows */\n\ttext-overflow: ellipsis;\n}\n```\n\nand that's it. You can find working pen [here](https://codepen.io/SassCrafter/pen/bGBPzvX?editors=0100)","user":{"name":"Dima Prohorenko","username":"sasscrafter","twitter_username":"SassCrafter","github_username":"SassCrafter","website_url":null,"profile_image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--6qbPa3bX--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_640,q_auto,w_640/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/492021/520f7947-9a2c-4a5a-98d6-cd662d3db8f4.jpeg","profile_image_90":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--43pRDxqZ--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_90,q_auto,w_90/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/492021/520f7947-9a2c-4a5a-98d6-cd662d3db8f4.jpeg"},"readingTime":"2 min read"}},"__N_SSG":true}